CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 8, 1941, pg. 17, reads: "Ossie Harris, local middleweight star, who will get his big chance Monday night at the Gardens when he squares off against tough Steve Belloise, leading title contender. After two weeks of stiff training, Ossie is set for the fight that may lead him to fame and fortune. - Staff photo by Harris."
TitMainTitle: Full length portrait of middleweight boxer Ossie Harris posed in front of brick wall of gymnasium
